saṃbuddhoktyanusāreṇa yatnābhāve tvapāyagaḥ | | (Śikṣāsamuccaya 19)

iti.

<commentary>yaduktam—sadā smṛtisaṃprajanyacāriṇā bhavitavyam iti, tataḥ smṛteḥ svanāmnaiva svarūpaṃ pratītam. saṃprajanyasya tu na jñāyate kīdṛśam iti tatsvarūpapratipattaye prāha.

yatkāyāvasthāyāḥ cittāvasthāyāś ca sarveryāpatheṣu pratyavekṣā nirūpaṇaṃ sarvavāraṃ yathā pratipāditaṃ prāk.</commentary>

sarvam etaduktaśikṣākauśalaṃ karmaṇā niṣpādayitavyaṃ na vacanamātreṇeti niyamayitum āha. manaḥpūrvaṃgamatvāt kāyavyāpārasya, so 'py anenaiva pratipāditaḥ. pratipattyā sarvaṃ saṃpādayiṣyāmi, na tu śabdamātraghoṣaṇayā niṣphalatvād iti bodhisattvena yatitavyam.